            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="grc">
                    <ab>
                        <lb n="1"/><unclear>Τ</unclear>ὸν λ<supplied reason="lost">α</supplied><unclear>μ</unclear>πρό<unclear>τ</unclear>α<unclear>τ</unclear>ο<supplied reason="lost">ν</supplied> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><unclear>ω</unclear>ι
                        <lb n="2"/>τὸν τοῦ ἱεροῦ <sic>πρετωρίου</sic> ἔπαρχον τοῦ δεσποτοῦ ἡμῶν
                        <lb n="3"/>Κωνσταντίου τοῦ Αὐγούστου καὶ Νικήτου καὶ τοῦ ἐπι<lb 
                            break="no" n="4"/>φανεστάτου Καίσαρος Ἰουλιανοῦ διʹ οὗ <sic>ἰρήνη</sic> καὶ ἀμεριμνία
                        <lb n="5"/>ὕπηρξεν ἡ Βατανέα τὸν εὐεργετὴν καὶ σωτήρα ἀνέστησεν,
                        <lb n="6"/>ἐπὶ <expan><abbr>Φλ</abbr><ex>αουίου</ex></expan> Μαξίμου τοῦ διασημοτάτου δουκηναρίου τοῦ σάλτου.
                    </ab>
            </div>
            <div type="apparatus">
                <p>Edition based on IGLS.</p>
                <p>
                    <app loc="2"><note>πραιτωρίου</note></app>
                    <app loc="4"><note>ἐιρήνη</note></app>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                <p>“Of clarissimus rank, ..., the prefect of the sacred praetorium of our master Constantius Augustus and Conqueror and of the most illustrious Caesar Julian, thanks to whom the peace and the security have existed, the Batanaea has erected (the statue of) the benefactor and saviour, under Flavius Maximus, the most eminent ducenarius of the saltus.”</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="fr">
                <p>“Le clarissime ... préfet du prétoire sacré de notre seigneur Constance Auguste et Vainqueur et du très illustre César Julien, par lequel paix et sérénité ont existé, la Batanée a érigé (la statue de) le bienfaiteur et sauveur, sous Flavius Maximus, le très éminent ducénaire du saltus.”</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="it">
                <p>“Il chiarissimo ..., prefetto del sacro pretorio di nostro signore Costanzo Augusto e Conquistatore e dell’illustrissimo Cesare Giuliano, grazie al quale la pace e la sicurezza sono esistite, la Batanea ha eretto (la statua del) benefattore e salvatore, sotto Flavius Maximus, l’eminentissimo ducenario del <foreign>saltus</foreign>.”</p>
            </div>
